=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612482\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cwt1665702639216.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cwt1665702639216.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cwt1665702639216.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cwt1665702639216\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Automatic Word Wrap\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether text is automatically wrapped to the next line when it exceeds the width of the widget. This also disables the horizontal scroll bar, if defined. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__section_w748ab1b5b1_w749ab1b5_w750ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Text that is too long for the widget width is automatically wrapped to the next line. The horizontal scroll bar, if specified, is disabled.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12038e1_d12039e1_d12040e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Long text is not wrapped.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__section_m5d_2ht_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d233874e127\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__table_d12041e1_d12042e1_d12043e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes for Edit Box</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Multiline</span> must be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__section_z4l_fht_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d233874e197\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__p_d102203e1_d102204e1_d102205e1\">When set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, automatic word\n            wrapping only works if the following conditions also apply:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__ul_qf4_ght_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__li_d41426e1_d41427e1_d41428e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__p_d102206e1_d102207e1_d102208e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Multiline</span> property\n                  is also <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__li_d41429e1_d41430e1_d41431e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__p_d102209e1_d102210e1_d102211e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Layout</span>\n                  should not include alignment codes <code class=\"ph codeph\">RGT</code> (Right-aligned) or\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">CTR</code> (Center-aligned ). (For a center-aligned field that\n                  contains a value longer than the field size, the contents are not scrolled to show\n                  the field value in the center of the field. )</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__p_d102212e1_d102213e1_d102214e1\">This property is not dynamic and cannot be set in\n            ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__section_j45_ght_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d233874e242\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__ul_z1t_jht_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__li_d42032e1_d42033e1_d42034e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cwt1665702639216__li_d42035e1_d42036e1_d42037e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqf1665702639504.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Multiline</a><p>This property determines whether the data in the widget is displayed on more than one line, and whether carriage returns can be used when entering data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612482\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612482\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Automatic Word Wrap Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Automatic Word Wrap Determines whether text is automatically wrapped to the next line when it exceeds the width of the widget. This also disables the horizontal scroll bar, if defined. True or False (default). Value Description True Text that is too long for the widget width is automatically wrapped to the next line. The horizontal scroll bar, if specified, is disabled. False Long text is not wrapped. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? Yes for Edit Box Dependencies: Multiline must be True Description When set to True , automatic word wrapping only works if the following conditions also apply: The Multiline property is also True . The Field Layout should not include alignment codes RGT (Right-aligned) or CTR (Center-aligned ). (For a center-aligned field that contains a value longer than the field size, the contents are not scrolled to show the field value in the center of the field. ) This property is not dynamic and cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To EditBox urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) Related Links Multiline This property determines whether the data in the widget is displayed on more than one line, and whether carriage returns can be used when entering data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}